<item>
            <title>[LU-19960] lnet: derive CPT locality from parent device for VLAN interfaces</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19960</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In multi-rail configurations using both physical and VLAN interfaces, only the rails&lt;br/&gt;
backed by physical devices may get selected due to missing CPT locality on the VLAN NIs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If possible, resolve VLAN devices to their underlying physical device and derive CPT&lt;br/&gt;
from the parent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
